<p>Tumblr isnâ€™t frame-free but itâ€™s the closest we have been in non-creator-originated-displays. The content doesnâ€™t look like it was filtered on its way out. In its chaos, it allows for more creativity.</p>

<p>Letâ€™s pause this line of thought and take a look at something in Paris.</p>

